Please try this out

open git bash and locate your BlogCode file within git bash

git checkout NugetBranch
git pull

cd CustomerSite
ls
should see no packages folder and should see a new .nuget folder

open CustomerSite.sln click run - should load webpages

Check the same for admin site


-----------------------------------------------------------------------------

Setting up NuGet for a project:

Right click on the solution in the solution expoler in VS

Click 'Enable NuGet Package Restore' 

Click 'yes'

You are then done :) 
